  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ 395°F/ Gas 6</p>\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Slice the<strong> potatoes</strong> into thin discs</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>potato discs</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiling water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 7-8 min or until almost tender</p>\n<p>Once done, drain, set aside to steam dry and reserve the pot</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cheesy-aubergine-and-lentil-moussaka/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim the green stalks off the<strong> aubergine<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and cut into quarters lengthways, then slice finely</p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>sliced aubergine</strong> and cook for 2-3 min on each side or until charred and beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cheesy-aubergine-and-lentil-moussaka/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\n<p>Transfer the <strong>softened aubergine</strong> to a plate and return the pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cheesy-aubergine-and-lentil-moussaka/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, re-boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic </strong></p>\n<p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>\n<p>Drain and rinse the<strong> canned lentils</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cheesy-aubergine-and-lentil-moussaka/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>ground cinnamon</strong> and cook for 30 sec</p>\n<p>Return the <strong>softened aubergine</strong> to the pan and add the <strong>drained lentils</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong></p>\n<p>Give everything a good mix up and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook until step 7</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cheesy-aubergine-and-lentil-moussaka/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat with 30g<span class=\"text-danger\"> [60g]</span> <strong>butter</strong></p>\n<p>Once melted, add 30g<span class=\"text-danger\"> [60g]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and stir with a wooden spoon for 1-2 min until a sandy paste forms – this is your<strong> roux</strong></p>\n<p>Gradually whisk 350ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [700ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> into the<strong> roux</strong>, a little at a time and cook for 5-7 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains</p>\n<p>Season generously with <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>béchamel sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cheesy-aubergine-and-lentil-moussaka/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the<strong> aubergine &amp; lentil mix</strong> to an<strong> oven-proof dish</strong></p>\n<p>Top with the <strong>drained potatoes</strong> then pour the<strong> béchamel sauce</strong> all over</p>\n<p>Grate the<strong> cheddar cheese</strong> all over and top with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p>\n<p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min until bubbling and golden</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> parsley</strong> roughly</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cheesy-aubergine-and-lentil-moussaka/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> aubergine &amp; lentil moussaka</strong> and garnish with the <strong>chopped parsley </strong></p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
